Sure, the error you're encountering is related to the way you're importing the Vite API in your `vite.config.js` file. The CommonJS (CJS) build of Vite's Node API is deprecated, and you should use the ECMAScript Module (ESM) build instead.

Here's an example of how you can update your `vite.config.js` file to use the ESM build:

```javascript
